INSERT INTO `shared_sitetext` VALUES (1,'about_text','<p>Our Group had started the operations in year 2008 and has become the leading remarketers, refurbishers and re-assemblers of Pre-owned Super Conductive MRIs and CT Scanners in India. Phantom Healthcare strives to provide professional support with quality services that are custom fit to the needs of today\'s growing healthcare industry. We are a reputed trader, supplier, exporter and importer of a wide range of MRI Scanner Systems, CT Scan Systems and related Parts and Accessories.</p>\r\n<p>As per the Director of the Company, Mr. Brijesh Suneja, the professionals of the company have dedicatedly offered the customers the products that comply not only with regulatory quality standards but also come well within client&rsquo;s budgets. \"Phantom Healthcare\" has emerged as a consistent performer and has successfully installed more than 50 Super-Conductive 1.5T MRIs across the country and in Nepal within a span of only 5 years. Trained engineers of the company have always satisfied the most challenging requirements of the customers and that&rsquo;s the reason company is enjoying the support of 50+ satisfied clients which provides testimony of our quality service standards.</p>\r\n<p>In this journey Phantom Healthcare have become strategic partners with M/s EverX PtyLtd. Australia which was established in year 1992, with a vision of establishing a complete International Medical Equipment Company with all kind of MRIs and CT sale, Service and Spare Parts Support. For the equipment funding issues, Phantom Healthcare does have support of leading financial institutions like Reliance Capital, HDFC, India Infoline etc. for resolving the funding needs of their clients.</p>','About Text at top of about page. A truncated version is shown at homapage'),(2,'sellcard_text','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> Quisque id tellus quis risus vehicula vehicula ut turpis. In eros nulla, placerat vitae at, vehicula ut nunc. </span></p>','Text Shown on the triggering cards of Sell Leadform'),(3,'buycard_text','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Quisque id tellus quis risus vehicula vehicula ut turpis. In eros nulla, placerat vitae at, vehicula ut nunc.</span></p>','Text Shown on the triggering cards of Buy Leadform'),(4,'partscard_text','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Quisque id tellus quis risus vehicula vehicula ut turpis. In eros nulla, placerat vitae at, vehicula ut nunc.</span></p>','Text Shown on the triggering cards of Parts Leadform'),(5,'servicecard_text','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Quisque id tellus quis risus vehicula vehicula ut turpis. In eros nulla, placerat vitae at, vehicula ut nunc.</span></p>','Text Shown on the triggering cards of Service Leadform'),(6,'videoslider_text','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\">Capacitance cascading integer reflective interface data development high bus cache dithering transponder.</span></p>','Text shown at top of video slider in home page'),(7,'videoslider_title_text','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">How MRI Works</span></p>','Title Text at the top of video slider'),(8,'leadform_text','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Join us for free &amp; get details on MRI Installation &amp; other Radiology Products.Just enter your details below.</span></p>','Top text on Lead Form which open on downloading brochure or clicking at Click here at home page'),(9,'buy_leadform_text','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Interested in a MRI? Phantom Healthcare needs to know a few things from you first!</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Do you prefer a certain manufacturer?</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Do you know what model?</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">What types of studies do you need a system to perform?</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">What budget range are you looking for?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Once we have your preferences we can give you a quote. If you are looking for more information please let us know in comment section.</p>\r\n<form class=\"leadform\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"form-group\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 10px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</form>','Top Text on top of Buy Lead Form'),(10,'sell_leadform_text','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Looking to Sell? You are at right place Phantom will buy your Equipment. We buy for our inventory, so we don&rsquo;t have to wait for a buying customer in order to pay for the equipment you are looking to sell. Feel free to do a price comparison, but we guarantee you that we are a reputable, knowledgeable source that can:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Establish fair market value for your system</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Work within your schedule</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Remove equipment in an efficient manner</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">Pay you as per our agreement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">If you are looking for more information please let us know in comment section.</p>','Text Shown At the top of Sell leadform Modal'),(11,'parts_leadform_text','<p>We keep MRI parts in stock, tested and ready for immediate shipment. Contact us today if you need MRI scanner parts for any of the following:</p>\r\n<table class=\"tablepattern2\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><th width=\"40%\">MRI Coils</th><th>GE MRI Parts- for 1.5T, 1.0T, 0.5T, 0.2T MRI Machines</th></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Head Coils</td>\r\n<td>RF Amplifiers</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Neck Coils</td>\r\n<td>Gradient Amplifiers</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Shoulder Coils</td>\r\n<td>Tables</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Spine Coils</td>\r\n<td>Other Parts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Breast Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Body Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wrist Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Extremity Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>CTL (Cervical, Thoracic, and Lumbar) Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Knee Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Surface Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Flex Coils</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Top Text Shown at top of parts leadform'),(12,'service_leadform_text','<p>Need Service or Repairs of your MRI? A one-stop service program that provides:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>High quality of service at prices significantly below the OEM\'s</li>\r\n<li>Service for all GE MRI Models</li>\r\n<li>Complete service from preventive to adhoc maintenance</li>\r\n<li>One Customer care number for all service/breakdown calls</li>\r\n<li>Immediate response from Service Engineer</li>\r\n<li>Flexible cost containment programs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Customer Friendly Service/Maintenance Packages - 24X7 Engineer Support</strong></p>','Text Shown at top of Service Leadform'),(13,'quality_card_text','<p>As a quality conscious organization, our sole aim is to provide the products with quality at par with global standards.</p>','Quality & Timely Delivery card text in about page'),(14,'refurbishing_card_text','<p>Engineered from grade A Liquid Helium, Super-conductive 1.5T MRI products are highly demanded in the market for being reliable</p>','Refurbishing card text in about page'),(15,'panindia_card_text','<p>Our engineers can assist with site plans and placement of your system for efficient use of space and successful installation of your system.</p>','Pan India Presence card text in about page'),(16,'financing_card_text','<p>For the equipment funding issues, Phantom Healthcare does have support of leading financial institutions like Reliance Capital,</p>','Easy Financing Card Text in about page'),(17,'quality_modal_text','<p>As a quality conscious organization, our sole aim is to provide the products with quality at par with global standards. Company&rsquo;s in-house swanky facility hosts ultramodern testing machinery and tools; and refurbishing process is supervised by a team of quality engineers. They work round the clock checking the products on the basis of regulatory parameters before they are sent to the clients. Moreover, they follow a well defined quality assurance policy in maintaining high upkeep standards. All the units are maintained as per laid government standards and are subjected to mandatory check-ups at regular intervals. Also a strict traceability is maintained right from the procurement of raw material to the packaging of finished goods.</p>','Text Shown in the Quality & Timely Delivery PopUp'),(18,'refurbishing_modal_text','<p>Engineered from grade A Liquid Helium, Super-conductive 1.5T MRI products are highly demanded in the market for being reliable and functionally efficient. Being the leader of the Third Party Refurbisher, our engineers restore used MRI equipment through repairing, reworking, updating and replacing of worn parts with original parts. All this is done to enhance the safety and effectiveness of the equipment. Our engineers also ensure that processes are consistent with product specifications and service procedures defined by the original manufacturer of the equipment. These actions ensure that the machines perform with the same quality standards as their new counterparts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>STEP 1: Selection</strong></p>\r\n<p>We carefully select only the very best, mid-life equipment for refurbishing. Our International Channel partner EverX takes the lead in this process. We avoid equipment that has experienced high usage or has been poorly maintained. That is the very reason; we only install Imported MRI machines for Indian Clients.</p>','Text Shown in the Refurbishing PopUp'),(19,'panindia_modal_text','<p><img src=\"/static/images/panmap.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>','Text Shown in the Pan India Presence PopUp'),(20,'financing_modal_text','<p>For the equipment funding issues, Phantom Healthcare does have support of leading financial institutions like Reliance Capital, HDFC, India Infoline etc. for resolving the funding needs of their clients. For the same purpose we ask Financial Institution to get in touch with client directly do the due-diligence of client\' profile and accordingly sanction the funding need.</p>','Text Shown in the Easy Financing PopUp'),(21,'address_info','<p><strong>ADDRESS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"adress\">PHANTOM HEALTHCARE <br />Plot No. 51, Sector 27C, Near NHPC Chowk, <br />Main Mathura Road, Faridabad, Haryana &ndash; 121 003 (INDIA)</li>\r\n<li class=\"mobile\">+91 129 4312423 <br />+91 9899112423</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"buisness\">Business Enquiry <br /> <a href=\"mailto:biz@phantomhealthcare.com\">biz@phantomhealthcare.com</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"recr\">Recruitment <br /> <a href=\"mailto:hr@phantomhealthcare.com\">hr@phantomhealthcare.com</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"info\">General Info <br /> <a href=\"mailto:info@phantomhealthcare.com\">info@phantomhealthcare.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Address in Contact Page');
